        "Desc": "Additionally consumes 1 Technique Points when characters use their Technique",
        "Story": "\"I've seen Emperor Rubert!\" Following the machine era calendar, on this day at nine in the evening, the invasive \"Wildminder\" entered the thoughts of a certain brain-in-a-jar in the Machine City. It was unable to distinguish whether itself was organic, inorganic, or just a gaseous lifeform. It claimed to have met the emperor, only to break away from the \"Wildminder\" in its head — The thought slammed the limits of its brain, overloading its thoughts to the point of exhaustion. But after Rubert fixed a single line of unmarkable code, it awakened from this haze, coming to realize that none of this had happened, that it had only been another illusion.",
